---
title: Festive Roast Lamb and Red Wine Jus with Roast Potatoes, Honey Glazed Root Veg and Mint Sauce
description: Celebrate this festive season with our Christmas inspired feast. This Festive Roast Lamb and Red Wine Jus is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
